y_John_Stephen_Smith" title="Henry John Stephen Smith">Henry John Stephen Smith</a> (1861)</span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/James_Joseph_Sylvester" title="James Joseph Sylvester">James Joseph Sylvester</a> (1883)</span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/William_Esson" title="William Esson">William Esson</a> (1897)</span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><strong class="selflink">Godfrey Harold Hardy</strong> (1920)</span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Edward_Charles_Titchmarsh" title="Edward Charles Titchmarsh">Edward Charles Titchmarsh</a> (1932)</span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Michael_Atiyah" title="Michael Atiyah">Michael Atiyah</a> (1963)</span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Ioan_James" title="Ioan James">Ioan James</a> (1969)</span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Richard_Taylor_(mathematician)" title="Richard Taylor (mathematician)">Richard Taylor</a> (1995)</span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Nigel_Hitchin" title="Nigel Hitchin">Nigel Hitchin</a> (1997)</span></p>
