gory:Old_Wykehamists" title="Category:Old Wykehamists">Old Wykehamists</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:1877_births" title="Category:1877 births">1877 births</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:1947_deaths" title="Category:1947 deaths">1947 deaths</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Royal_Medal_winners" title="Category:Royal Medal winners">Royal Medal winners</a></span></div></div>			<!-- end content -->
